---
title: Oven Baked Greek Style Meatballs with Orzo and Veggies
description: On the Greek island of Corfu, meatballs are traditionally served with fragrant rice. Mimi has mixed them up with an Italian twist of orzo, which is a rice shaped pasta - a perfect accompaniment to both hot
or cold dishes (makes great leftovers for lunch!).
